{"tid":2173621,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高文喪call球員 古天奴有得留低","createTime":"2020-08-25T10:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T15:48:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c30685abe9ea67a2a131908f5443231b0a5a8b87","tid":2173621,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】西班牙傳媒指，巴塞隆拿新教練朗奴高文近期忙於致電告知球員去留，其中古天奴將重返球隊。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙《世界體育報》稱，剛為拜仁慕尼黑奪得歐聯冠軍的古天奴（Philippe Coutinho），周一收到巴塞隆拿新教練朗奴高文的電賀，並獲通知新球季可獲重返魯營，希望一起為重建球隊而努力。<br />\n<br />\n古天奴收到的是電賀，但更多人收到的卻是噩耗，烏拉圭球星蘇亞雷斯、維達爾已知道將被棄用，其餘將離隊的球員還有安迪堤、拉傑迪、菲普等。<br />\n<br />\n至於青訓產品的巴斯基斯、碧基、沙治羅拔圖則前途未卜，後衛艾巴則肯定留在陣中，與他向來默契甚佳的美斯，繼續領軍迎接新球季，為剛過去一季3大皆空，包括衛冕西甲失敗及在歐聯被拜仁慕尼黑大敗，撥亂反正。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"6c7eea21e2442cec1d64d39ca217028924d652f1","tid":2173621,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"球盲分別器 走唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c14a46e61ea44e05d4b322d68769e00102bc608","tid":2173621,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"古sir值得巴塞為佢起一座銅像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1b3b67ca61d693dcc10a15eb84adf3de994dba","tid":2173621,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:58:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac4eda292fd8ab595eb0d02a277a1b6b07e21e9d","tid":2173621,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:59:31.000Z","msg":"M<del>SN</del>"},{"pid":"6f9714648f7f090ffab44ee432f3be699e249c5d","tid":2173621,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"以為係kinglsy coman<img src=\"/assets/faces/